Concept actor
----------------------------------------------------------------

Topic . 1 Actors

T . The actors

Topic index 2 Functions

T . An actor is like a function call to a class, except the call is to the run time engine.
T . The actor commands has access to the class functions and variables.
T . The actor is like a function overload that instead of having different functions for the data types, it has a overload that matches variables in the class.
T . It behaves like an advanced case statement with multiple matches.

Topic var 2 Actor variables

T . The actor match has access to the same variables as the commands in the actor has.

Topic flow 2 Actor flow

T . Multiple actors of the same name can match, and the Break command stops any further matches.

Topic cmd 2 Actor commands

T . The Du, All, Its, This and That commands call other actors.


